description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Leisha shares some secret tips on buying a television. Kate, however, already bought a television so the advice is a bit moot. They then share their favorite ways to be tortured via massage.
